red-light time controlled by rotary encoder
yellow-light time is a steady five seconds
green light time is whatever red-light time - yellow-light time leaves left with a minimum of 1
mode shifted by pushbutton on rotary encoder

four modes:
	alternating
	NS stopped
	EW stopped
	4-way stop

targets to switch:
	NS_red
	NS_yellow
	NS-green
	EW_red
	EW_yellow
	EW_green


